latestIgtvVideos.title: The Leela Goa ( part 1)
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Introducing this fabulous property adjoining the cleanest beach of south Goa 🏝 This has to be one of the finest property I have stayed in recent times . It has been a wholesome & luxurious experience indeed . They have all the best amenities.. 80 acres property with a private beach , club house , lush green lawns , poolside bars , beachside shacks , rooms with plunge pool , gorgeous lagoons & 4 restaurants and many many more . It wasn’t possible for me to capture this entire resort in one day hence the rest shall be continued in my next video 🤍

Gave it a watch if you’re bored &looking to see some nature & serenity bit in south Goa !!!!! 
.
.
